{"tid":1811534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以話我知我係咪鍾意佢或者應唔應該開始","createTime":"2020-01-04T18:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T03:32:14.000Z","uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"646f5e4dd0ff9a99194115c08d72bbbfeb2d91d6","tid":1811534,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的 有個男仔A  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中一至中三好frd <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中三果年我鍾意左佢 同佢表白之後佢拒絕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中四 我同另一個男仔 B <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拍拖 就冇再同A 聯絡 拍到中五B送左頂帽俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hurt 到就黎死 A就黎我講番野 tum 我 tum吓 tum吓佢自己鍾意左我 過左2個月同我表白 但我對佢冇feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能失戀對我打擊太大 中五同中六既時候 我成個人被扭曲左 特別係我既性取向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我鍾意左女仔F F係我同A既common frd 所以我一直冇同A講 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家 Year 1<br />\n<br />\nF 最近去左外國讀書 可以少左好多聯絡 佢番到黎我覺得又唔係好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不嬲都有同A 2個人出開街 今日同另外一對情侶出 之後見到A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個電話 有個佢番工既女人問佢今日去左邊度挽 之後我同佢講 人哋有仔架喎 頌問你既 之後佢話佢都想溝人 果吓個心好乸 後尾A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />送我番屋企 我問佢頌有冇鍾意我 佢話有少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA係對愛情好認真既人 每次鍾意人都1年以上 宜家頌係A0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪鍾意佢或者試吓開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一切同我個名冇直接關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b361621d558dce8bc1b811cfd8450fc6b5c2e210","tid":1811534,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T18:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人可以理吓我"},{"pid":"05b3d71482bc857802ce1f0a4b4a48bb63a2ef3c","tid":1811534,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T19:10:02.000Z","msg":"放過人啦"},{"pid":"91e77f39b0842063c8b24ca208a9f67cf1a8123a","tid":1811534,"uid":204750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T19:37:27.000Z","msg":"咪害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee633bfe03e5d1c9004fa7d78cfa3cd97b3d62f","tid":1811534,"uid":111181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfd7c0f5c982d271094b79907688a6d101b6ace","tid":1811534,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"1a07b2d9fffdfc2bd8bc88a073b9071cf94d40eb","tid":1811534,"uid":288780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:07:43.000Z","msg":"係有Feel先好開始"},{"pid":"26a3beffa2aa4b374b387099507f21731b524469","tid":1811534,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee633bfe03e5d1c9004fa7d78cfa3cd97b3d62f","tid":1811534,"uid":111181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}